des:
"WRDJ 93.5 FM is an outreach ministry of Calvary Chapel Merritt Island, Florida.
Broadcasting since 2006, WRDJ airs good, solid Bible teaching, contemporary Christian music,and news and local interview programs.

WRDJ is a non-profit, non-commercial radio station, supported primarily by the people of Calvary Chapel Merritt Island, offering hope, salvation and encouragement through the ministry of the Word of God…Jesus is the Word! "
